headline: DoorDash CFO to Participate in Fireside Chat at Upcoming Investor Conference
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, November 12, 2024--DoorDash, Inc. (NASDAQ: DASH) today announced that Ravi Inukonda, Chief Financial Officer, will participate in a fireside chat at the Nasdaq 51st London Investor Conference on Tuesday, December 10th, 2024, at 1:30 pm GMT.
